name: Desmonema
description:
Desmonema is part of the Micrographia series that takes inspiration from the early explorers of the microscopic world. These artworks have been crafted with thoughtful insight and tender loving care. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs. 

Size : 3698x6031px PNG [bitmap image]
2021 | Mark Webster @motiondesign_01
